.e1197rjj0{填充-top:0.375rem;}}</style>;<div class="css-1m7l96h e18kpe851">;<figure class="css-sscfcz e1197rjj0">;<img loading="lazy" width="608" height="626 “解码=“异步”data-nimg=“1”样式=“颜色：透明”尺寸=“300px”srcset=“https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=16，质量= 80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 16w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=32，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images /20240330_EPC030.png 32w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=48，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 48w，https://www .economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=64，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 64w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/宽度=96，质量=80，格式=自动/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 96w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=128，质量=80，格式=自动/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 128w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=256，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 256w ，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=360，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 360w，https://www.economist.com/ cdn-cgi/image/width=384，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 384w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=480，quality =80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 480w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/图片/20240330_EPC030.png 600w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=834，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 834w，https:// www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 960w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image /width=1096，quality=80，format=auto/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 1096w，https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1280，quality=80，format=自动/content-assets/images/20240330_EPC030.png 1280w，https://www.economist.com/cdn